Transcription.Text: Once again it was being demonstrated that the Terran life- form suffers from ye fear of wette paynt. The first smearer would have ten years willed off his unfortunate life. It was in these conditions, in mid-afternoon of the second day, that McNaught's bones proved their feelings had been prophetic.
